INSERT INTO
    ocean_climate (
    timestamp,depth,latitude,longitude,water_speed,water_direction,upward_sea_velocity,wind_speed,wind_direction,salinity,temperature,sea_floor_depth
   )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::TIMESTAMPTZ[],$2::INT[],$3::DECIMAL[],$4::DECIMAL[],$5::DECIMAL[],$6::DECIMAL[],$7::DECIMAL[],$8::DECIMAL[],$9::DECIMAL[],$10::DECIMAL[],$11::DECIMAL[],$12::DECIMAL[]
    )
        ON CONFLICT (timestamp,depth,weather_location_id) DO NOTHING
